{"tid":2415410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"TVB 係咪又出有問題既新聞？","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:10:59.000Z","uid":51200,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2162f6f669554dce3341badeb36ef9c16502f28f","tid":2415410,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u22LEFt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu22LEFt.png&h=f88b333a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvAQQNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvAQQNa.png&h=ba667c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/world/60301309335d19a043e769ae/研究指單劑復必泰疫苗最高效力達85-降新冠病毒傳播率\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F60301309335d19a043e769ae%2F%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%96%AE%E5%8A%91%E5%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E6%B3%B0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E5%8A%9B%E9%81%9485-%E9%99%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E7%8E%87&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=df2f9ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/world/60301309335d19a043e769ae/研究指單劑復必泰疫苗最高效力達85-降新冠病毒傳播率</a><br />\n<br />\n以色列明明用緊嘅係Biontech +輝瑞批出既疫苗<br />\n一般叫「輝瑞疫苗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間並無中國復星醫藥參與嘅成份，<br />\n難道唔係只有大中華地區既Biontech疫苗可以叫做「復必泰」咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><br />\n政府認可復星醫藥/德國藥廠BioNTech的新冠疫苖在香港作緊急使用，預計下月下旬由德國運抵香港。復星醫藥及BioNTech發表聯合聲明，指會密切配合特區政府的疫苗接種計劃，確保市民能早日接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，疫苗的中文名為「復必泰」。<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572320-20210126.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572320-20210126.htm&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=ff3a6e25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572320-20210126.htm&h=8598bd1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572320-20210126.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n「復必泰」叫「復必泰」係因為中國復星醫藥子公司上海復星醫藥產業發展有限公司於2020年3月獲德國BioNTech SE授權，負責該疫苗在中國大陸及港澳台地區的臨床試驗、上市申請和市場銷售，並承擔相應的成本和費用。<br />\n<br />\n不過，以色列用嗰隻係美國輝瑞直接批架啵，支疫苗完全無中國復星參與嘅成份，咁又點會叫復必泰？你可以叫BNT162/ Biontech/輝瑞疫苗，但叫復必泰錯架下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話就話無論以色列定香港都好都係用緊輝瑞+Biontech既BNT162，但以色列用嘅版本同大中華地區唔同ga bor <br />\n復必泰只係大中華地區用嘅版本<br />\n所以話以色列用「復必泰」，係咪可以投訴假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n誤導觀眾以為香港用嘅中國復星「復必泰」版本，同以色列用嘅係一樣野"},{"pid":"c0ecffff925fec7a9eaae8d52311d0815d9447a8","tid":2415410,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"d01584e1288552f94e6b7e9cf7077e5ee07c97ae","tid":2415410,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"d3fc9664e69381c7e80f2e53e4abbee48ad0a81a","tid":2415410,"uid":389053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78301c838f5a685409df43b40ba31afdc34d7871","tid":2415410,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"推到TVB改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceb689b55d1ebe67e9b57fcbc14a0